OL,3,CBride-to-be suffers serious injuries
OL,4,Cafter explosion in Paris nightclub
OL,6,FA bride-to-be has been critically
OL,7,Finjured following an explosion at a
OL,8,Fpopular Paris nightclub.
OL,10,FFfion Price, of Brynmawr, was
OL,11,Fcelebrating her hen do in the French
OL,12,Fcapital when the "horrific" accident
OL,13,Foccurred.
OL,15,FThe incident at Pachamama nightclub
OL,16,Fwas caused by the explosion of the
OL,17,Fbattery of an electric scooter that
OL,18,Fwas being stored on the fourth floor
OL,19,Fof the building.
