OL,3,CBride-to-be suffers serious injuries
OL,4,Cafter explosion in Paris nightclub
OL,6,FThe explosion, which occurred shortly
OL,7,Fbefore midnight on Saturday, 6 July,
OL,8,Fcaused parts of the club ceiling and
OL,9,Fwalls to collapse.
OL,11,FThree people were injured, Welsh bride-
OL,12,Fto-be Ffion amongst them.
OL,14,FShe remains in hospital in Paris,
OL,15,Fwhere she is receiving treatment for
OL,16,Fher serious injuries ahead of her
OL,17,Fwedding in just over a month.
