OL,3,CBride-to-be suffers serious injuries
OL,4,Cafter explosion in Paris nightclub
OL,6,FA GoFundMe page has been set up by a
OL,7,Ffamily member to support Ffion and her
OL,8,Ffiance Chris while she remains in
OL,9,Fintensive care.
OL,11,FThe page described how Ffion suffered
OL,12,Fa fractured skull, a fracture in her
OL,13,Fear, a bleed on the brain which
OL,14,Frequired immediate surgery and a
OL,15,Fhospital stay in intensive care, as
OL,16,Fwell as surgery to her face.
