OL,3,CBride-to-be suffers serious injuries
OL,4,Cafter explosion in Paris nightclub
OL,6,FThey said: "Ffion remains in a
OL,7,Fhospital in Paris with her family by
OL,8,Fher side and is not expected to return
OL,9,Funtil at least next week.
OL,10,FUnderstandably, Ffion and her family
OL,11,Fare distraught, especially since she
OL,12,Fand her fiance Chris are due to get
OL,13,Fmarried next month.
OL,15,F"I am hoping to raise money to support
OL,16,FFfion's family with transport and
OL,17,Faccommodation whilst out in Paris. I
OL,18,Fam also hoping to make Ffion's return
OL,19,Fhome as comfortable as possible and to
OL,20,Faid her recovery so she can marry the
OL,21,Flove of her life in just six weeks."
